Deep in the ocean on the Mid atalntic ridge, an energy bubble travels 
at high speeds with its sole Occupant, Darkfate. The bubble begins to 
climb higher in the water till it reaches its destination, a large 
MEtal struture that seems to be spidering out into other structures. 
Outside along each building multiple construction drones work 
building towers of energy, the entire place glowing ominously. The 
bubble slows its speed and soon enters a large building at the center 
of all this, all water being cut off by an energy field. Once inside 
the bubble fizzles out and drops Darkfate onto the floor as an 
Orangish bot walks up to him accompanied by what appears to be a 
black skeleton with a large green energy field built around it.

Hooligan: "Summon your men..."
